---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Kakarrot — AI 产品经理的经历与原则" canonical="/about/" shell>
  <div style={{padding: "38px 30px", borderBottom: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)", display: "flex", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "flex-end"}}>
    <div>
      <h1 style={{fontSize: "var(--text-section-title)", letterSpacing: "var(--ls-section-title)", lineHeight: "var(--lh-section-title)", fontWeight: 900, margin: "0 0 8px"}}>关于</h1>
      <p style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 var(--font-mono)", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", margin: 0}}>Kakarrot &mdash; AI 产品经理的经历与原则</p>
    </div>
    <p style={{font: "400 14px/1.4 var(--font-mono)", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", margin: 0, whiteSpace: "nowrap"}}>自救者、人恒救之</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-2 reveal" style={{display: "grid", gridTemplateColumns: "1fr 1fr", borderBottom: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>
    <section style={{padding: "38px 30px", borderRight: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>
      <h2 style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 var(--font-mono)", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", marginBottom: "14px"}}>经历</h2>
      <p style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, margin: "0 0 12px"}}>
        PM，坐标郑州。暴雪粉，音乐狂，收集癖，强迫症。
      </p>
      <div style={{fontSize: "15px", lineHeight: 1.7, color: "var(--color-text-secondary)"}}>
        <p style={{margin: "0 0 8px"}}><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>2020 前</strong> — 积累具体做事方法、工作经验，养成阅读、写作习惯。</p>
        <p style={{margin: "0 0 8px"}}><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>2020 后</strong> — 系统地梳理总结产品专业知识，沉迷于阅读、写作。</p>
        <p style={{margin: 0}}><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>2022 后</strong> — 认识 AI、拥抱 AI、学习 AI、研究 AI。</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section style={{padding: "38px 30px"}}>
      <h2 style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 var(--font-mono)", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", marginBottom: "14px"}}>原则</h2>
      <ul style={{listStyle: "none", padding: 0, margin: 0}}>
        <li style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, marginBottom: "8px"}}>先理解问题，再设计方案。</li>
        <li style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, marginBottom: "8px"}}>技术是手段，不是目的。</li>
        <li style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, marginBottom: "8px"}}>最好的产品是那些用户感觉不到的产品。</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-2 reveal reveal-delay-2" style={{display: "grid", gridTemplateColumns: "1fr 1fr"}}>
    <section style={{padding: "38px 30px", borderRight: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>
      <h2 style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 var(--font-mono)", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", marginBottom: "14px"}}>桌面 · 2024</h2>
      <ul style={{listStyle: "none", padding: 0, margin: 0, fontSize: "15px", lineHeight: 1.8, color: "var(--color-text-secondary)"}}>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>CPU</strong> Intel i5-13600kf</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>主板</strong> Asus TUF B760M-PLUS WIFI II</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>显卡</strong> Asus TUF RTX 4070 SUPER O12G</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>内存</strong> Corsair 16G×2 DDR5 6400</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>固态</strong> Samsung 980PRO 1T + TiPlus7100 2TB</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>散热</strong> DeepCool AK620</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>电源</strong> Phanteks AMP GH850W</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>机箱</strong> NZXT S340 Elite</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>解码</strong> OCTAVART Champs-élysées + HD650</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>音箱</strong> Bose C50</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>键盘</strong> Filco 圣手二代 104 / Cherry G80-3000</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>鼠标</strong> Logitech G903 + Master 3</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>显示</strong> LG 34UC88-B + LG 27GR84Q-B</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>耳机</strong> Sennheiser HD650 + Logitech G933</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>路由</strong> Phicomm K3C</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section style={{padding: "38px 30px"}}>
      <h2 style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 var(--font-mono)", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", marginBottom: "14px"}}>移动 · 2023</h2>
      <ul style={{listStyle: "none", padding: 0, margin: 0, fontSize: "15px", lineHeight: 1.8, color: "var(--color-text-secondary)"}}>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>笔记本</strong> MacBook Air M5 24G+1T</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>显示</strong> Aoc U32N3C</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>键盘</strong> NIZ T-35g C103 / IKBC Poker Pro 61</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>鼠标</strong> Logitech Master 3 / MX Vertical</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>耳机</strong> Bose QC35 II</li>
        <li><strong style={{color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>阅读</strong> Kindle Paperwhite 4</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
